WSL Support
~~~~~~~~~~~
If you are using Windows Subsystem for Linux, you need to run this command to visualize the results:

.. code-block::

  Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux
